{
  "stem": "19441.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 390.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I will steal some potatoes from the kitchen and I will cooks for you and so-- and that will help you-- for that work what you did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was the work?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the toilets was very far and they didn't-- and it was very dark and didn't let people go there, so there was wheelbarrows and people finished themself in the wheelbarrow.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the wheelbarrow was full, they took it early in the morning to the latrine and they spilled it over and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was her duty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the SS man came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he came to me, so I quickly-- oh, so quick like I don't know how could I manage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, I am night shift, but if you want I jump out from bed and I will do my duty.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, shut up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that minute saved my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The others didn't have that excuse, so all the 29 girls went to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In a few days, they will be all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what happened with me, I had-- because I had that paratyphus, so I lost my vision.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't hear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they just lifted me up like sack of potatoes and I dropped me wherever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sing I could, so I was always singing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a good voice then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if somebody came, they just kicked me, so I knew be quiet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That means be quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so in charge of this barrack was a German woman, non-Jewish German woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, I can't keep her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's not good for anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I sent her to the gas chambers, because otherwise I am responsible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the girls from the group says, listen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can sew.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
